diagrams.mermaid:
flowchart TD
  Start([新診斷 Epithelial Ovarian Cancer]) --> Imaging[CT abdomen/pelvis<br>CA125 / HE4<br>biopsy or paracentesis cytology]

  Imaging --> Stage{Stage 評估}

  Stage -->|Stage I 局限| Surg_I[Primary staging surgery<br>TAH+BSO+omentectomy<br>+ peritoneal washing + LN sampling<br>Fertility-sparing 可選 IA low-grade]

  Stage -->|Stage II-IV| Resectable{可達 R0?<br>PS / 瘤量 / CT 預測}

  Resectable -->|是| PDS[**Primary Debulking Surgery (PDS)**<br>目標 R0<br>切除腹膜瘤、omentum、bowel<br>含 retroperitoneal LND]

  Resectable -->|否| NACT[**Neoadjuvant Chemo × 3 cycles**<br>Carbo AUC 5-6 + Pac 175 mg/m²<br>Q3W]

  NACT --> IDS[**Interval Debulking Surgery (IDS)**<br>± HIPEC (OVHIPEC-1)<br>cisplatin 100 mg/m² 42°C × 90 分]

  IDS --> Chemo3[再 chemo × 3 cycles]

  PDS --> Adj_Chemo[Adjuvant Pac/Carbo × 6 cycles<br>Q3W<br>Stage IC-IV high-grade 必加]

  Surg_I --> Risk_I{Risk?}
  Risk_I -->|IA low-grade| Obs[Observation 或<br>adjuvant chemo × 3]
  Risk_I -->|IC / IB-II high-grade| Adj_Chemo

  Adj_Chemo --> Mol_Test[BRCA + HRD testing<br>+ tumor markers monitor]
  Chemo3 --> Mol_Test

  Mol_Test --> Maint([前往 2️⃣ Maintenance 樹])

  classDef early fill:#d4edda,stroke:#27ae60;
  class Surg_I,Obs early;
  classDef mid fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#c89a3a;
  class PDS,NACT,IDS mid;
  classDef sys fill:#f8d7da,stroke:#c0392b;
  class Adj_Chemo,Chemo3 sys;

flowchart TD
  Start([完成 1L Pac/Carbo × 6<br>CR / PR]) --> BRCA{BRCA1/2 mutation<br>germline + somatic}

  BRCA -->|BRCA mut<br>~15-20% HGSC| BRCA_path[**SOLO-1 path**<br>Olaparib 300 mg BID × 2 yr<br>5-yr PFS 48% vs 21%<br>Cat 1]

  BRCA -->|BRCA wild-type| HRD{HRD status<br>Myriad myChoice / FoundationOne}

  HRD -->|HRD+<br>non-BRCA<br>~30%| HRD_path[**PAOLA-1 path**<br>Olaparib + Bevacizumab<br>Bev 15 mg/kg Q3W × 22 cycles<br>+ Olap 300mg BID × 2 yr<br>PFS 37.2 vs 17.7 月]

  HRD -->|HRP / HRD-<br>~50%| HRP_path[**PRIMA path** 或<br>**Bev maintenance only**]

  HRP_path --> Choice{選擇}
  Choice -->|不論 biomarker| Nira[**PRIMA**<br>Niraparib 200-300 mg QD × 3 yr<br>PFS 13.8 vs 8.2 月<br>HRP subgroup HR 0.68]
  Choice -->|Bev 起家 1L| Bev_alone[**Bev maintenance**<br>GOG-218 / ICON7<br>15 mg/kg Q3W × 22 cycles<br>high-risk subgroup OS+]

  BRCA_path --> FollowUp[追蹤<br>CA125 + CT Q3M × 2yr<br>之後 Q6M]
  HRD_path --> FollowUp
  Nira --> FollowUp
  Bev_alone --> FollowUp

  classDef brca fill:#d4edda,stroke:#27ae60;
  class BRCA_path brca;
  classDef hrd fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#c89a3a;
  class HRD_path hrd;
  classDef hrp fill:#f0e8ff,stroke:#7a5aa8;
  class Nira,Bev_alone hrp;

flowchart TD
  Start([Recurrent ovarian cancer]) --> PFI{Platinum-Free Interval}

  PFI -->|>6 月<br>Platinum-Sensitive| PS_path[**Platinum-Sensitive 重新挑戰 platinum**]
  PFI -->|≤6 月<br>Platinum-Resistant| PR_path[**Platinum-Resistant 換 non-platinum 後線**]

  PS_path --> PS_choice{Regimen 選擇}
  PS_choice --> PS_PldCarbo[**Carboplatin + PLD**<br>CALYPSO<br>較 Carbo/Pac 副作用低]
  PS_choice --> PS_GemCarbo[**Carboplatin + Gemcitabine** ± Bev<br>OCEANS / GOG-213]
  PS_choice --> PS_CarboPac[**Carbo + Paclitaxel** ± Bev<br>AGO-OVAR-2.5]

  PS_PldCarbo --> PS_Maint{Response + BRCA?}
  PS_GemCarbo --> PS_Maint
  PS_CarboPac --> PS_Maint

  PS_Maint -->|BRCA mut| SOLO2[**SOLO-2** Olaparib maintenance<br>PFS 19.1 vs 5.5 月]
  PS_Maint -->|HRD+ / 不論| ARIEL3[**ARIEL3** Rucaparib<br>或 **NOVA** Niraparib<br>maintenance]

  PR_path --> PR_choice{FRα status?}
  PR_choice -->|FRα-high IHC PS2+| MIRASOL[**Mirvetuximab soravtansine**<br>MIRASOL trial<br>OS 16.5 vs 12.8 月 HR 0.67<br>FDA 2024 完全批准]
  PR_choice -->|FRα low / 不適合| PR_chemo[**單藥化療**:<br>PLD 40-50 mg/m² Q4W<br>Topotecan 4 mg/m² weekly<br>Weekly paclitaxel 80 mg/m²<br>Gemcitabine ± Bev AURELIA]

  PR_chemo --> Salvage[後線 salvage:<br>Trabectedin + PLD<br>Etoposide PO<br>Hormone if ER+<br>Clinical trial]
  MIRASOL --> Salvage

  classDef ps fill:#d4edda,stroke:#27ae60;
  class PS_path,PS_PldCarbo,PS_GemCarbo,PS_CarboPac ps;
  classDef pr fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#c89a3a;
  class PR_path,PR_chemo pr;
  classDef adc fill:#f0e8ff,stroke:#7a5aa8;
  class MIRASOL adc;
